        "email": "elena.gryaznova@hpe.com",
        "username": "elena"
      },
      "date": "2017-05-30 16:51:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nHello James, Minh, Yujian.\n> So, IMHO, since the changes have been tested by Elena\n\nWe use ha.sh for failover/failback tests on real HW including NEO3.x (IEEL). The issues we hit are reported in SEA tickets. Patch for master is not tested on HW. But sure, i can install master build to our real client and attach the results to LU ticket.\nPlease let me know if this is reasonable.\n\nThanks.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
